<p class="p">Moisture content was determined using the method as described by AOAC (2016) [
 <xref rid="B21-plants-08-00051" ref-type="bibr" class="xref">21</xref>]. An empty crucible was dried to a constant weight in an oven at 105 °C, allowed to cool in a desiccator and weighed (
 <italic class="italic">W</italic>
 <sub class="sub">1</sub>). The pulverized plant sample (2.0 g) was weighed (
 <italic class="italic">W</italic>
 <sub class="sub">2</sub>) in the crucible and dried at 105 °C until it attained a constant weight. The crucible containing the plant sample was allowed to cool in a desiccator and the weight (
 <italic class="italic">W</italic>
 <sub class="sub">3</sub>) was measured. The moisture content was calculated in percentage thus as: 
 <disp-formula id="FD1-plants-08-00051" class="disp-formula">
  <math id="mm1" class="math">
   <mrow class="mrow">
    <mrow class="mrow">
     <mo class="mo">%</mo>
     <mo class="mo"> </mo>
     <mi class="mi">M</mi>
     <mi class="mi">o</mi>
     <mi class="mi">i</mi>
     <mi class="mi">s</mi>
     <mi class="mi">t</mi>
     <mi class="mi">u</mi>
     <mi class="mi">r</mi>
     <mi class="mi">e</mi>
     <mo class="mo"> </mo>
     <mi class="mi">c</mi>
     <mi class="mi">o</mi>
     <mi class="mi">n</mi>
     <mi class="mi">t</mi>
     <mi class="mi">e</mi>
     <mi class="mi">n</mi>
     <mi class="mi">t</mi>
     <mo class="mo">=</mo>
     <mfrac class="mfrac">
      <mrow class="mrow">
       <msub class="msub">
        <mi class="mi">W</mi>
        <mn class="mn">2</mn>
       </msub>
       <mo class="mo">−</mo>
       <msub class="msub">
        <mi class="mi">W</mi>
        <mn class="mn">3</mn>
       </msub>
      </mrow>
      <mrow class="mrow">
       <msub class="msub">
        <mi class="mi">W</mi>
        <mn class="mn">2</mn>
       </msub>
       <mo class="mo">−</mo>
       <msub class="msub">
        <mi class="mi">W</mi>
        <mn class="mn">1</mn>
       </msub>
      </mrow>
     </mfrac>
     <mo class="mo">×</mo>
     <mfrac class="mfrac">
      <mrow class="mrow">
       <mn class="mn">100</mn>
      </mrow>
      <mn class="mn">1</mn>
     </mfrac>
    </mrow>
   </mrow>
  </math>
 </disp-formula>
</p>
